{"type":null,"faqId":48073,"title":"天气","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.p1{margin-left:1.18125in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:-0.110416666in;margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:1.18125in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p4{margin-bottom:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:1.4409722in;margin-top:0.027777778in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:9pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.41527778in;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>天气应用不仅方便您查看当前位置的天气信息，还可查看世界各地当天以及未来几天的天气信息。</span><a name=\"_task_add_city_weather-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">添加城市</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>将关心的城市添加到天气界面，可以方便及时查看这些城市的天气信息。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"增加城市\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span>在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 天气”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">2.  </span><span>点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178092\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178093\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，输入要添加的城市名称，搜索栏下方会列出相匹配的城市列表。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">3.  </span><span>点击要添加的城市。</span><a name=\"_task_check_city_weather-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">查看天气</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"查阅天气\"XE \"城市天气\"XE \"空气质量\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 天气”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.左右滑动屏幕，切换到要查看的城市，查看当地天气情况。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178094\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，查看更多天气指标。</span><a name=\"_task_delete_city_weather-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">删除城市</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"删除城市\"XE \"移除城市\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 天气”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178095\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，长按要删除的城市，然后点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178096\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178097\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”。</span><a name=\"_task_refresh_weather-chtext\"></a>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">更新天气</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>XE \"手动更新天气\"XE \"定时更新天气\"XE \"自动更新天气\"</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>1.在主屏幕，点击“实用工具 &gt; 天气”。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2.左右滑动屏幕，切换到要更新天气的城市。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3.向下滑动屏幕，手动更新天气。</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178098\" style=\"width:0.5in;height:0.16597222in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>您可以将天气设置为自动更新模式。点击“</span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178099\" style=\"width:0.22916667in;height:0.16319445in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span> &gt; </span><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=178100\" style=\"width:0.22777778in;height:0.16666667in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><span>”，打开“自动更新”开关，设置“更新间隔”，手机将按照设定的时间间隔定期刷新天气。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":1094,"faqType":"生活助手","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"3659","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Convenient-features","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1445598111000,"seriesProductName":"RIO-AL00,RIO-CL00,RIO-TL00,RIO-UL00,RIO-UL10","visitedTimes":66,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":null,"avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}